msgctxt "104_Hana"
msgid "Oh, Chief. I'm so glad I caught you. "
msgstr "Ah, jefe. Menos mal que contestó. "

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "Why? What's up? "
msgstr "¿Por qué? ¿Pasó algo? "

msgctxt "128_Hana"
msgid "There's a customer who wants to see you. "
msgstr "Hay un cliente que desea reunirse con usted. "

msgctxt "140_Hana"
msgid "It seems kind of important. Can you come back to the office? "
msgstr "Parece algo importante. ¿Podría regresar a la oficina? "

msgctxt "152_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, hang tight. I'll be there as soon as I can. "
msgstr "... Va, va. Iré tan pronto como pueda. "

